Well I had a really scary week and its only Wednesday ... On Monday morning a at 5:09 Am a police officer called my house to tell me and my mom that my brother was in a car accident involving 3 cars and hes was in the hospital! We rushed there and he was in a neck brace with a broken nose, bruises all over, blood all over him, and a burnt face from the air bag.It happened at about midnight that night his friend that was driving was drunk and hit 2 cars before hitting a 3rd car head on! He was then knocked out! Im sorry I really havent been around for the past couple of days, but thats why! The people at the hospital are suprised he is still alive .... Hes fine now though thank God! It really put my lifein perspective though and things that I cared so much about before mean nothing to me anymore! Thank you for the support of the peopple that were there for me through it and the people that I know will be for me after this ... Im just thankful kenny is out of the hospital and walking around! I dont wanna leave his side... So far I got the best Christmas persent ever ... My Brother ALIVE! I love you all and I promise to tell you this when ever I see and speak to youo from now on ... You never know when your time will come!!!
